author: Second Wind
description:
Spoiler warning: This video contains narrative and visual spoilers for Episodes 1-4 of Scarlet Hollow.

In this episode of Storycraft, Jess chats with Abby Howard and Tony Howard-Arias about writing Scarlet Hollow’s dynamic cast of characters and creating the game’s nuanced relationship system.

Music used in order of appearance:
Scarlet Hollow – Scarlet Hollow OST
Greenpath – Hollow Knight OST
Night Market – Stardew Valley OST
North Coast 500 – Burnhouse Lane OST
Mines (Star Lumpy) – Stardew Valley OST
Gestral Market – Clair Obscur: Expedition 33 OST
The Lost Village of Docarri (Day) – Sea of Stars OST
Some Place Far Away (Feat. Dan Zappulla) – Scarlet Hollow OST
